=Analyze the following lost item and compare it with the found items below. Identify all potential matches and return a JSON array with this exact format:

[
  {
    "index": 0,
    "isMatch": true,
    "confidence": 85,
    "reasoning": "Item names are very similar, same class, and descriptions match"
  },
  {
    "index": 1,
    "isMatch": false,
    "confidence": 0,
    "reasoning": "Different item classes and names don't match"
  }
]

Only include items where isMatch is true and confidence is 60 or higher.

{{ $json.lostItemText }}

---

Found Items to Compare:

{{ $json.foundItemsText }}

Return ONLY valid JSON array, no other text.

